data.title: Gave birth in 2006
data.text:
7.3 0

Melissa Joan Hart gave birth to son Mason Walter Wilkerson on the 11th of January 2006. Mason is the first child of Hart and husband Mark Wilkerson, they also share two other sons: Braydon Hart Wilkerson (born 2008) and Tucker (born 2012).

7.2 0

Holly Hunter gave birth to twin boys, reportedly named Claude and Press, on the 17th of January 2006. The twins are the first and second child respectively for Hunter and partner Gordon MacDonald.

7 0

Brody Dalle gave birth to daughter Camille Harley Joan Homme on the 17th of January 2006. Camille is the first child of Dalle and husband Josh Homme they also share a son: Orrin Ryder (born 2011).

6.3 0

Amanda Holden gave birth to daughter Alexa Louise Florence Hughes on the 21st of January 2006. Alexa is the first child of Holden and husband Chris Hughes; they also share another daughter Hollie Rose (born 2012).

7.6 0

Angela Bassett gave birth to twins Slater Josiah and Bronwyn Golden on the 27th of January 2006. The twins are the first and second child respectively for Bassett and husband Courtney B. Vance.

6.9 0

Joely Fisher gave birth to daughter True Harlow on the 2nd of February 2006. True is the second child for Fisher and husband Christopher Duddy, they also share another daughter Skylar Grace (born 2001). The couple adopted a daughter in 2008, they named the newborn Olivia Luna Fisher-Duddy. Duddy has two children from a previous marriage, Cameron (born 1984) and Collin (born 1986).

8.1 0

Christy Turlington gave birth to son Finn on the 11th of February of 2006. Finn is the second child for Turlington and husband Edward Burns, they also share a daughter Grace (born 2003).

7.4 0

Renée O'Connor gave birth to daughter Iris Sura O'Connor on the 19th of March 2006. Iris is the first child for O'Connor and partner Jed Sura. O'Connor has one child from a previous marriage: Miles William Muir (born 2001).

7.6 0

Melania Knauss gave birth to son Barron William Trump on the 20th of March 2006. Barron is the first child for Knauss and husband Donald Trump. Trump is also the father of four other children, Donald John Trump Jr. (born 1977), Ivanka Marie Trump (born 1981), Eric F. Trump (born 1984) and Tiffany (born 1993).

7.1 0

Rhea Durham gave birth to son Michael on the 21st of March 2006. Michael is the second child for Durham and now-husband Mark Wahlberg, they share three other children, daughters Ella Rae (born 2003) and Grace Margaret (born 2010) and son Brendan Joseph (born 2008).

6.8 0

Gwyneth Paltrow gave birth to son Moses Bruce Anthony Martin on the 8th of April 2006. Moses is the second child for Paltrow and husband Chris Martin, they also share a daughter Apple Blythe Alison Martin (born 2004).

7.7 0

Gena Lee Nolin gave birth to son Hudson Lee Hulse on the 15th of April 2006. Hudson is the first child for Nolin and husband Cale Hulse, they also share a daughter Stella Monroe Hulse (born 2008). Nolin has a son from a previous marriage, Spencer Fahlman.

6.7 0

Katie Holmes gave birth to daughter Suri Cruise on the 18th of April 2006. Suri is the first child for Holmes and husband Tom Cruise. Cruise has two adopted children from a previous marriage, Isabella Jane (born 1992) and Connor Antony (born 1995).

7.6 0

Brooke Shields gave birth to daughter Grier Hammond on the 18th of April 2006. Grier is the second child for Shields and husband Chris Henchy, they also share another daughter Rowan Frances (born 2003).

7.6 0

Summer Sanders gave birth to daughter Skye Bella on the 21st of April 2006. Skye is the first child for Sanders and husband Erik Schlopy, they also share another child Robert Charles Spider Schlopy (born 2008).

7.6 0

Karen Elson gave birth to daughter Scarlett Teresa White on the 2nd of May 2006. Scarlett is the first child for Elson and husband Jack White. They also share another child, son Henry Lee White (born 2007).

6.5 0

Jackie Sandler gave birth to daughter Sadie Madison Sandler on the 6th of May 2006. Sadie is the first child for Sandler and husband Adam Sandler, they also share another daughter: Sunny Madeline Sandler (born 2008).

7.5 0

Alex Curran gave birth to daughter Lexie on the 9th of May 2006. Lexie is the second child of Curran and husband Steven Gerrard, they also share two other daughters: Lilly-Ella (born 2004) and Lourdes (born 2011).

8.1 0

Sasha Alexander gave birth to daughter Lucia Sofia on the 12th of May 2006. Lucia is the first child of Alexander and husband Edoardo Ponti, they also share a son: Leonardo Fortunato (born 2010).

6.5 0

Geri Halliwell gave birth to daughter Bluebell Madonna Halliwell on the 14th of May 2006. Bluebell is the only child of Halliwell and an unnamed father.

7.6 0

Lea Salonga gave birth to daughter Nicole Beverly on the 16th of May 2006. Nicole is the first child for Salonga and husband Robert Charles Chien.

7.2 0

Gwen Stefani gave birth to son Kingston James McGregor Rossdale on the 26th of May 2006. Kingston is the first child for Stefani and then-husband Gavin Rossdale. They had two other sons, Zuma Nesta Rock Rossdale (born in 2008) and Apollo Bowie Flynn (born 2014). Rossdale has one child from a previous relationship, Daisy Lowe, born 1989.

7.7 0

Angelina Jolie gave birth to daughter Shiloh Nouvel Jolie-Pitt on the 27th of May 2006. Shiloh is the first biological child for Jolie and husband Brad Pitt. In 2008 Jolie gave birth to twins Knox Léon and Vivienne Marcheline. Pitt and Jolie are also the parents of three adoptive children, Maddox Chivan (born 2001), Pax Thien (born 2003) and Zahara Marley (born 2005).

7 0

Mira Sorvino gave birth to son Johnny Christopher King on the 29th of May 2006. Johnny is the second child of Sorvino and husband Christopher Backus, they also share three other children Mattea Angel (born 2004), Holden Paul Terry Backus (born 2009) and Lucia (born 2012).

8.1 0

Rachel Weisz gave birth to son Henry Chance on the 31st of May 2006. Henry is the only child for Weisz and then-fiancé Darren Aronofsky.

7.9 0

Nadia Comaneci gave birth to son Dylan Paul Conner on the 3rd of June 2006. Dylan is the first child for Comaneci and husband Bart Conner.

6.8 0

Brandi Chastain gave birth to son Jaden Chastain Smith on the 8th of June 2006. Jaden is the first child for Chastian and husband Jerry Smith. Smith also has one child from a previous relationship, Cameron (born around 1991).

7 0

Tanya Haden gave birth to son Samuel Jason Black on the 10th of June 2006. Samuel is the first child of Haden and husband Jack Black, they share another son Thomas David (born 2008).

5.3 0

Luciana Barroso gave birth to daughter Isabella on the 11th of June 2006. Isabella is the first child for Barroso and husband Matt Damon, they also share two other children, Gia Zavala Damon (born 2008) and Stella Zavala Damon (born 2010). Barroso also has a child from a previous marriage, Alexia.

7.3 0

Elisabeth Shue gave birth to daughter Agnes Charles Guggenheim on the 18th of June 2006. Agnes is the third child of Shue and husband Davis Guggenheim, they also share two other children Miles William (born 1997) and Stella Street (born 2001).

7.8 0

Mariska Hargitay gave birth to son August Miklos Friedrich Hermann on the 28th of June 2006. August is the first child for Hargitay and husband Peter Hermann, they adopted a daughter Amaya Josephine in 2011 and another son, Andrew Nicolas shortly afterwards.

7.2 0

Danielle Spencer gave birth to son Tennyson Spencer Crowe on the 7th of July 2006. Tennyson is the second child for Spencer and husband Russell Crowe, they also share another son Charles Spencer Crowe (born 2003).

6.6 0

Anna Nicole Smith gave birth to daughter Dannielynn Hope Birkhead on the 7th of September 2006. Dannielynn is the only child of Smith and ex-boyfriend Larry Birkhead. Soon after Dannielynn's birth Smith was found dead of a apparent drug-overdose. Smith had one child from a previous relationship, Daniel Wayne Smith (born 1986, died 2006).

6.1 0

Britney Spears gave birth to son Jayden James Federline on the 12th of September 2006. Jayden is the second child of Spears and ex-husband Kevin Federline, they also share another son Sean Preston Federline (born 2005). Federline also has two other children from a previous relationship, Kori Madison (born 2002) and Kaleb Michael (born 2004) and one from a latter, Jordan (born 2011).

6.6 0

Anna Gunn gave birth to daughter Eila Rose Duncan on the 12th of September 2006. Eila is the second child for Gunn and husband Alastair Duncan, they also share another daughter: Emma (born 2001).

6.3 0

Rachael Bella gave birth to son Ethan Page Furlong on the 21st of September 2006. Ethan is the only child for Bella and then-husband Edward Furlong.

7.7 0

Jessalyn Gilsig gave birth to daughter Penelope on the 26th of September 2006. Penelope is the only child of Gilsig and then-husband Bobby Salomon.

7.6 0

Jennie Garth gave birth to daughter Fiona Eve on the 30th of September 2006. Fiona is the third child of Garth and then-husband Peter Facinelli, they have two other daughters, Luca Bella (born 1997) and Lola Ray (born 2002).

7.1 0

Maggie Gyllenhaal gave birth to daughter Ramona on the 3rd of October 2006. Ramona is the first child for Gyllenhaal and husband Peter Sarsgaard; they also share another daughter, Gloria Ray who was born in 2012.

7.8 0

Linda Evangelista gave birth to son Augustin James on the 11th of October 2006. Augustin is the only child of Evangelista and ex-boyfriend François-Henri Pinault who has a daughter from a later marriage; Valentina Paloma (born 2007).

6.9 0

Molly Parker gave birth to son William Strummer Bissonnette on the 13th of October 2006. William is the first child for Parker and husband Matt Bissonnette.

6.8 0

Kelly Rutherford gave birth to son Hermés Gustaf Daniel Giersch on the 18th of October 2006. Hermés is the first child for Rutherford and then-husband Daniel Giersch, they also share a daughter: Helena Grace Rutherford Giersch (born 2009).

7.9 0

Holly Marie Combs gave birth to son Riley Edward Donoho on the 26th of October 2006. Riley is the second child of Combs and husband David Donoho, they also share two other sons, Finley Arthur Donoho (born 2004) and Kelley James Donoho (born 2009).

7.6 0

Nicole Ari Parker gave birth to Nicolas Neruda Kodjoe on the 31st of October 2006. Nicolas is the second child of Parker and husband Boris Kodjoe, they also share a daughter: Sophie Tei-Naaki Lee Kodjoe (born 2005).

7.9 0

Gillian Anderson gave birth to son Oscar on the 1st of November 2006. Oscar is the first child for Anderson and partner Mark Griffiths, they also share another son Felix (born 2008). Anderson has another child from a previous marriage, Piper Maru (born 1994).

7.6 0

Kellie Martin gave birth to daughter Margaret Heather Christian on the 4th of November 2006. Margaret is the first child for Martin and husband Keith Christian.

7.3 0

Heidi Klum gave birth to son Johan Riley Fyodor Taiwo Samuel on the 22nd of November 2006. Johan is the second child of Klum and then-husband Seal, they also share two other children, Henry Gunther Ademola Dashtu Samuel (born 2005) and Lou Sulola Samuel (born 2009). Klum also has a child from a previous relationship, Helena Samuel (born 2004) who Seal has adopted as his own child.

9 0

Erica Hill gave birth to son Weston Robert Yount on the 25th of November 2006. Weston is the first child for Hill and husband David Yount, they also share another son: Sawyer Steven Yount (born 2010).

7.6 0

Sofia Coppola gave birth to daughter Romy on the 28th of November 2006. Romy is the first child for Coppola and partner Thomas Mars, they also share another child: Cosima (born 2010).
